st element of _possibleInstantsBefore_.             1. Let _offsetNs_ be GetNamedTimeZoneOffsetNanoseconds(_systemTimeZoneIdentifier_, _disambiguatedInstant_).           1. Let _offsetMs_ be truncate(_offsetNs_ / 10&lt;sup&gt;6&lt;/sup&gt;).           1. Return _t_ - 𝔽(_offsetMs_).         ">
